{"tid":485570,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發] 港大已被赤化為「中国香港大学」\"The University of Xianggang\"","createTime":"2017-12-01T05:24:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-21T13:16:46.000Z","uid":132968,"like":12,"dislike":142,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"30bddd779c321a699322b61b789c7c6ff695f351","tid":485570,"uid":132968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T05:24:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">主張面向中國　爭取北京資助</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n美籍內地學者　張翔接任港大校長</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/01/132231_6cb9df03d0cfe043b171aff300fe0d8a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F01%2F132231_6cb9df03d0cfe043b171aff300fe0d8a.jpg&h=623d6583&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【蘋果日報】港大敲定新校長人選。據了解，該校遴選委員會昨拍板選定美籍內地學者、專研納米科學工程的張翔出任新校長。據悉校委會主席李國章昨在會議上稱曾與其他委員私下討論，結論是入圍的兩名英美外籍學者都不適合港大，委員會最終選擇倡議與內地合作的張翔。<br />\n<br />\n消息稱，張在交予委員會的建議書中建議港大應重視科研、<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">面向中國</span></span>，提到清華、北大科研出色是源於獲得中國政府大量資助，因此<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">港大應主動與中國不同大學合作</span></span>，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">並接觸中國教育部以獲中央資助</span></span>，發展科研。至於該名港大現任教職員候選人，則建議港大發展人文社會學科，稱香港在《基本法》保護下，可進行更多相關內地研究。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，委員會討論期間，大部份成員均認同張的方向，更有委員指<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「香港的未來在中國」</span></span>，因此看重張於內地科研聯繫；同時不認同在港大任教的候選人建議，因他未有將重點放予中國，不適合港大。經兩小時討論，委員以7比4票落實由張出任新校長。現時港大校長年薪連福利約660萬至675萬元。港大發言人接受《蘋果》查詢時僅稱會適時公佈新校長人選。<br />\n港大教師及職員會主席張星煒稱，早料李國章會出手操控校長遴選，結果不出所料，港大人難指望張翔捍衞學術及院校自主，「一個人（張翔）如果淨係講funding（撥款），佢根本唔會講院校自主、學術自由，亦唔會夠膽講」。他質疑張欠大學行政經驗，「馬斐森嚟港大前都做過院長，佢只係一個系主任」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171201/20231289\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171201%2F20231289&d=cygn4Wa%2FmKpL8v96hwkPUQCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=1ca378ad\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171201%2F20231289&h=495ca5b9\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171201/20231289</a><br />\n<br />\nOmg... <del>HKU</del> XGU's new headmaster is fighting for funding from Chinese central government... The Fall of HKU... I mean XGU... <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nCan you imagine what will XGU become after this?..."},{"pid":"bbdf381c44bbb87f28de22d5f8b4dd05156845b2","tid":485570,"uid":810,"like":47,"dislike":1,"score":46,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T05:26:07.000Z","msg":"XGU<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fab147b2a17ff904909bb461779bc263fec6740f","tid":485570,"uid":132968,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T05:36:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> HKU -&gt; XGU"},{"pid":"1636ed792b4b115dfdd27c7471b9c04a31c7776e","tid":485570,"uid":11818,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T05:38:01.000Z","msg":"Xgu 買衫架"},{"pid":"def0bd1b199e2e532d18bedc285474b8648a9b12","tid":485570,"uid":132968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T05:50:19.000Z","msg":"No one cares about this?"},{"pid":"4564076a02e86cfff285ffd9f949d604b61907b4","tid":485570,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T05:53:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>No one cares about this?</blockquote><br />\nIs"},{"pid":"08d84d90b6804261d2315c986d8307b44c2077a2","tid":485570,"uid":132660,"like":71,"dislike":0,"score":71,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T05:56:47.000Z","msg":"咩xgU 係xgdx啊"},